oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pre-Columbian human head figurine
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Pre-Columbian ceramic figure depictng a human face with a prognathic nose. The figure is wearing a head dress and ear plugs. Details on the eyes, mouth, ear plugs, and head dress are incised.
The top of the figure's head dress is chipped on both sides.
